2011-06-27T07:08:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/u-k-stocks-are-little-changed-astrazeneca-lloyds-man-group-shares-fall.html
U.K. stocks recouped losses, leaving
the benchmark FTSE 100 Index little changed at 5,698.67 as of
8:09 a.m. in  London . The gauge had dropped as much as 0.3
percent at the market open.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
